divs: Sighting DetailsRiding 4 wheeler atv ..came around bend and there was a ufo to my left at apx 75' high and it was reflecting the sky sort of like the predator movie. it just blinked out. it was a sort of rectangle, after it blinked out I went to top of the mountain and saw a silver object going across the valley at apx 3 miles. I dont know if they were the same object. I didnt really mention the event for a long time like my brain couldnt belive what I saw.
Summary: Saw UFO that looked like part of the sky.
